Package thatslife

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionCard
    This class defines the ActionCard object.
    ActionDeck
    This class is the container that initializes and holds all ActionCards.
    BlueCard
    This class defines the BlueCard object.
    BlueDeck
    This class is the container that initializes and holds all ActionCards.
    BlueSpace
    This space inherits from the Space class and prompts the user to draw a BlueCard, upon playerLand.
    Card
    This Card class does not do anything but state the abstract method event.
    CareerCard
    This class defines the CareerCard, which inherits from the Card class.
    CareerDeck
    This class is the container of the CareerCards.
    CareerPath
    This class is a container for all spaces that belong to the career path.
    ChangeCareerPath
    This class is a container for all spaces that belong to the change career path.
    CollegePath
    This class is a container for all spaces that belong to the college path.
    Deck
    This is the abstract superclass of all the card deck classes in the game.
    EndSpace
    This class defines the final space that players will land on, which is the retirement space.
    GreenSpace
    This class represents the space for Pay Day or Pay Raise.
    GUIMain  
    HouseCard
    This class holds the data for the houses in the game.
    HouseDeck
    This class defines the container for all house cards.
    JunctionSpace
    This class defines the JunctionSpace, which is a MagentaSpace that prompts the user to decide where to go.
    MagentaSpace
    This class defines MagentaSpace, a type of space that requires the player to stop moving and execute its events.
    Map
    Main Map class.
    OrangeSpace
    This class defines the most common space in the game, the OrangeSpace.
    Path
    This class defines the structure blocks of the game, the paths.
    Player
    This is the Player class.
    SalaryCard
    This class contains the details about a player's salary.
    SalaryDeck
    This class defines the container for the SalaryCards.
    Space
    This class defines the very building-block of the game, the Space.
    StartFamilyPath  
    StartSpace
    This class defines the StartSpace, the starting point (insertion point) of all players in the game.
    ThatsLife
    That's Life (inspired by the board game "The Game of Life") This class is the master That's Life game class.
    Transaction
    This class defines the structure for a transaction that will be done and recorded by each instance of player.
